/>\n但木遁本質就冇乜特別<br />\n你見大和呢個人辦就知<br />\n即使靠基因植入血繼 但都係冇乜大作為"},{"pid":"d406016000fd5bccd23a9c20fbae8d48cd5066ef","tid":882603,"uid":155253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T19:50:10.000Z","msg":"其實千手一族去哂邊 點解末落左 冇哂人"},{"pid":"22afa74b58de2a4dff524cb7606160164a5c7bc8","tid":882603,"uid":43839,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"852ffd3ac28a42cbc651b05a529074d0feb67806","tid":882603,"uid":141869,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a2aab8746adab66e2f0bb99ccff23bc164d46044","tid":882603,"uid":29880,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:37:20.000Z","msg":"因為佢係六道個仔轉世"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:39:37.000Z","msg":"鳴人夠係，唔見佢用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T19:59:14.000Z","msg":"陣之書中表示鳴人可以是用木遁在體內壓制九尾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f37a27de3191de69be53528c8583c2e53da07cf","tid":882603,"uid":43839,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ee3bc6057da5d53a4dab5c59b0296f5fdd613aab","tid":882603,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"6cab37e45cdad33ba843e017491e16b48847ab8a","tid":882603,"uid":25635,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:07:38.000Z","msg":"有呢個血統都唔代表開到呢個能力架喎<br />\n秋道家都係等勁耐先出得到丁次可以唔食藥蝶化<br />\n日向同宇治波都唔係個個開寫輪眼同白眼能力啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:38:54.000Z","msg":"咁至少佢地家族都唔只一人用到，<br />\n依家木盾得一個喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T20:01:36.000Z","msg":"wiki 話<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">可以用木遁的有：十尾（神樹）、白絕、阿修羅、 柱間、斑、大和、段藏、帶人（黑絕只是用白絕的身體發動木遁）、萌黃</code></pre>"},{"pid":"fb08feb3657e89758d85cbc8c40b172b695c8b2b","tid":882603,"uid":24188,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T20:02:16.000Z","msg":"係因為一般人剩係用到一種屬嘅查克拉<br />\n而柱用到土+水=木"},{"pid":"37be3df17f4cf65623b55ed474682ba461e7e3d5","tid":882603,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score"